document_data.name: Rathal Evanara
document_data.mainbody: '''Rathal Evanara''' was the high priest of the [[Temple of Corellon Larethian]] in [[Leuthilspar]] on the island of [[Evermeet]].
document_data.History: Around [[1369 DR]], Evanara was responsible for running the temple and maintaining the building and its grounds with the help of two acolytes.
